# BLACKBOX — Session Handoff

## Project
- **Name:** BLACKBOX (Obsidian-Cortex Agentic OS)
- **Repo:** https://github.com/blitzcrieg1/agentic-os (private), branch `master`
- **Head:** `219242c` — IVT + deferred autonomous resume
- **Wedge:** Governed autonomy — LangGraph state machines, approval gates, vault ledger, mission-control dashboard

## Local-first (non-negotiable)
- **Windows 11**, developer PC only — no cloud deploy
- Orchestrator `localhost:8000`; dashboard dev `localhost:3000` (or 3001)
- **No Docker** default; Gemini API = only cloud dependency
- Secrets: `apps/orchestrator/.env` (gitignored)
- **Preferred run:** `scripts\blackbox.bat start` or `scripts\serve.bat` (single process)

## Run locally
```powershell
# Single process (recommended)
scripts\serve.bat

# Dev (two terminals)
cd apps\orchestrator && uvicorn api.main:app --reload --port 8000
cd apps\dashboard && npm run dev
```

## Stack
- `apps/orchestrator/` — FastAPI, LangGraph, AsyncSqliteSaver, APScheduler, vault watcher, `blackbox` CLI
- `apps/dashboard/` — Next.js 14, React Flow, Zustand, WebSocket
- `vault/` — skills in `.system/skill-definitions/`, triggers in `.system/trigger-rules/`
- **Skills (3):** lead_gen, summarize_meeting, weekly_review — hand-edited Python graphs + registry

